Mbali cheye hachidaha bule kudaya chochose chochilondeka kutenda, mbali chizatenda ivo muladi chidaya chetu chifike muna ichipindi Mulungu choyachilongele cheye, na muna ichipindi icho na mweye iviya chifika kumwenu.
