Waleka kumwetu, mbali wakala wanhu siyo wetu bule. One wakala wanhu wetu, wahadahile kukala na cheye. Mbali viyalawilile, yalawilila fana viya habule munhu yoyose muna dibumbila jetu yoyalagusigwe kuwa kakala miyetu.
