Habule kudumba muna dilondo, mbali ulondo wokomelezeka wowinga kudumba, kwaviya kudumba kohita na nhaguso, na munhu yoyose yoodumba hafaya kugendelela na ulondo wake.
Cheye chomulonda kwaviya yeye kawalonda cheye teng'hu.
